  "detailed_description": "<h1>Take a late-night ride in Synthwave Tunnel!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376640/extras/6b5ffe6bf7068514b8e494dc0c7d1ddc.avif?t=1772361625\" width=600 height=190 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Take a late-night ride in Synthwave Tunnel! Race through neon-lit, rhythm-generated paths, pushing your reflexes to the limit. Speed through dynamic obstacles, synced to the beat, and conquer the ultimate challenge. Can you reach the end?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376640/extras/d0965fc19325d81d06b0a6b061eb57ab.poster.avif?t=1772361625\" width=600 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376640/extras/d0965fc19325d81d06b0a6b061eb57ab.webm?t=1772361625\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376640/extras/d0965fc19325d81d06b0a6b061eb57ab.mp4?t=1772361625\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About Synthwave Tunnel</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Race through the neon-lit world of Synthwave Tunnel, where each beat shapes the path ahead. Dodge obstacles, stay in sync with the rhythm, and test your reflexes in this high-speed challenge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376640/extras/7c87687a707734bfd9203c3153b88bdc.poster.avif?t=1772361625\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376640/extras/7c87687a707734bfd9203c3153b88bdc.webm?t=1772361625\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376640/extras/7c87687a707734bfd9203c3153b88bdc.mp4?t=1772361625\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With vibrant visuals and dynamic gameplay, Synthwave Tunnel delivers an intense mix of rhythm and action. Can you master the music and reach the end?</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Take a late-night ride in Synthwave Tunnel! Race through neon-lit, rhythm-generated paths, pushing your reflexes to the limit. Speed through dynamic obstacles, synced to the beat, and conquer the ultimate challenge. Can you reach the end?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376640/extras/d0965fc19325d81d06b0a6b061eb57ab.poster.avif?t=1772361625\" width=600 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376640/extras/d0965fc19325d81d06b0a6b061eb57ab.webm?t=1772361625\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376640/extras/d0965fc19325d81d06b0a6b061eb57ab.mp4?t=1772361625\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About Synthwave Tunnel</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Race through the neon-lit world of Synthwave Tunnel, where each beat shapes the path ahead. Dodge obstacles, stay in sync with the rhythm, and test your reflexes in this high-speed challenge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376640/extras/7c87687a707734bfd9203c3153b88bdc.poster.avif?t=1772361625\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376640/extras/7c87687a707734bfd9203c3153b88bdc.webm?t=1772361625\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376640/extras/7c87687a707734bfd9203c3153b88bdc.mp4?t=1772361625\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragra